	<section id="intro">
		<div class="descriptions">
			<h2>Sentiment</h2>
			<p>Emotional Securities is a behavioral investing tool. We apply new technology to the decades old framework of contrarian value investing. Positive sentiment is measured on a scale of 0 to 1. Negative sentiment is between 0 and -1. </p>
		</div>
		<div class="descriptions">
			<h2>Markets</h2>
			<p>Any value based strategy needs informed financial metrics. We pull real-time stock information including pricing and volume everytime we analyze market sentiment. This lets us build a platform grounded in reality.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="descriptions">
			<h2>Careful Data</h2>
			<p>Opening the internet floodgates to gauge sentiment is tricky. We care deeply about the quality of our data. We filter incoming articles and tweets with a Bayes Classifier that persists in our application. It categorizes every new piece of text as useful or wasteful.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

